high_descs: Walk forward then turn left and look down at the ground.
Pick up the baseball bat off of the ground.
Turn around and walk up to the end of the bed.
Put the wooden bat on the left side of the bed.
anns.task_desc: Move a wooden bat from the ground to a bed.

high_descs: Take a step forward then turn left.
Pick up the baseball bat that's in front of you on the floor.
Turn around and walk to the bed.
Lean the bat on the bed against the wall to the left of the book with the handle on the top.
anns.task_desc: Put a bat on the bed.

high_descs: Take one step then turn left and look down at the floor.
Pick up the baseball bat on the floor.
Turn to the right and walk to the bed.
Place the baseball bat on the left side of the bed.
anns.task_desc: Carry the baseball bat to the bed.
